              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Construction is the expertise of erecting structures, from basic shelters to formidable stone fortresses. Masters of this craft understand materials, engineering, and tool use to build sturdy defenses or breach enemy walls. In a magical world, construction might weave in enchanted stones for resilience or runes to repel mystical threats. This skill is essential for adventurers seeking to create safe refuges or dismantle obstacles in their path.",
